name: Data Science
body:
### Welcome to Resources for Data Science.

Do you want to become a data scientist using R or Python? Here you will find resource for data science including programs, webpages, books, reference cards, list, cheatsheets, libraries and datasets.

If you consider that some resources are missing, let me know and contact me!
